title: By His Majesty's company, at the Theatre Royal in Drury-Lane, this present Saturday, March 4, 1780, The old batchelor : with alterations ... to which will be reviv'd in 2 parts (the 27th time) the pantomime entertainment of Fortunatus, with alterations and three entire new seasons ... To conclude with a representation of the storming Fort Omoa, in the Bay of Honduras
